      "raw": "Let page width/height be \\(W,H\\). Safe content rectangle subtracts margins \\(m\\) (all sides) and bleed \\(b\\): \\[ W_s = W - 2(m+b), \\quad H_s = H - 2(m+b) \\] With gutters \\(g_x, g_y\\), rows \\(r\\), cols \\(c\\), aspect \\(a = \\frac{w}{h}\\) (if fitting by aspect): \\[ w_{\\max} = \\min\\!\\left(\\frac{W_s - (c-1)g_x}{c},\\; a\\cdot\\frac{H_s - (r-1)g_y}{r}\\right), \\quad h_{\\max} = \\frac{w_{\\max}}{a} \\] For fixed print size \\((w_p,h_p)\\), grid feasibility requires: \\[ c\\,w_p + (c-1)g_x \\le W_s,\\quad r\\,h_p + (r-1)g_y \\le H_s \\] Mat border \\(b_m\\) grows each print to: \\[ w_m = w_p + 2b_m,\\quad h_m = h_p + 2b_m \\] Waste percent uses page safe area \\(A_s=W_sH_s\\) vs. used area \\(A_u = n\\,w_m h_m\\): \\[ \\text{Waste} = \\max\\!\\left(0,\\;1 - \\frac{A_u}{A_s}\\right)\\times 100\\% \\]"
